Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,---------------------------------PREV-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.04,0:00:05.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和纯一趁着暑假参加了巴士旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.74,0:00:09.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由于玩得太欢而遭到了报应
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.81,0:00:12.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在被人丢在了公路的服务区
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.37,0:00:16.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然不应该吃那个鳗鱼茶套餐的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.47,0:00:19.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你意思是怪我咯？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.92,0:00:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纯一你不也吃了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.01,0:00:23.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话是这样说…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.51,0:00:25.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 别把责任推到我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.91,0:00:26.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我哪有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.84,0:00:28.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还说没有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.51,0:00:38.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那时我们还无法想像
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.41,0:00:44.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们身上接下来将会发生什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.49,0:02:18.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那还真是倒霉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.64,0:02:22.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 没想到会被丢在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.13,0:02:27.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薰对限定商品和本地特产太没抵抗力了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.35,0:02:28.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要继续说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.66,0:02:31.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不也说过「能吃到实在太好了」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.56,0:02:33.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有是有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.46,0:02:37.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但完全没想过薰会把时间弄错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.40,0:02:39.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然已经考虑到时间可能弄错了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.07,0:02:43.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就应该严厉地警告我这样不好才对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.43,0:02:46.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是看你当时很想吃…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.64,0:02:48.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你别只责怪我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.74,0:02:50.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁都没责怪你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.80,0:02:52.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这口气不就是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.59,0:02:54.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就到此为止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.46,0:02:57.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是羡煞旁人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.38,0:02:59.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.73,0:03:03.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓越是吵架关系越好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.73,0:03:07.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之按刚才说好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.42,0:03:09.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,送你们到附近的车站
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.48,0:03:11.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有劳了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.11,0:03:13.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实在很不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.37,0:03:17.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没记错的话 车站旁有一家温泉旅馆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.86,0:03:19.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚你们就住那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.45,0:03:21.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.44,0:03:24.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是所谓的山间温泉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.22,0:03:26.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面很淳朴 感觉挺不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.24,0:03:29.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温泉…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.76,0:03:44.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纯一 水温怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.72,0:03:50.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.29,0:03:52.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.68,0:03:58.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纯一？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.43,0:04:00.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.56,0:04:01.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.13,0:04:05.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然那么喜欢 就这样定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.14,0:04:06.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.83,0:04:09.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 还好你们不是单独出游
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.82,0:04:14.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俗话说出门在外靠朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.11,0:04:17.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像旅途上有个伴儿能使人放心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.98,0:04:23.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,互助互爱的人情味在人世间是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.96,0:04:34.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.91,0:04:35.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实在是帮了我们大忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.64,0:04:39.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见 别再吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.82,0:04:48.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他人真好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.65,0:04:49.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.36,0:04:54.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 所推荐的温泉旅馆是走这边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.80,0:05:03.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.78,0:05:06.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.28,0:05:17.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那进去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.14,0:05:18.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.37,0:05:25.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.18,0:05:27.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会是害怕了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.52,0:05:31.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这 这点小事怎么会害怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.33,0:05:39.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薰？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.93,0:05:42.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.01,0:05:47.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你被吓到了吧 刚才
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.62,0:05:50.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你平常连游乐园的尖叫游戏都不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.58,0:05:53.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说 薰你害怕了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.60,0:05:56.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才没有害怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.11,0:05:58.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才只是装作被吓到的样子而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.90,0:06:00.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.97,0:06:08.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二位愿意的话可以先去沐浴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.67,0:06:10.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是天然温泉来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.20,0:06:12.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.83,0:06:18.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天店内只有您二位客人 请慢慢享受
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.59,0:06:26.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里给人的感觉有点阴森
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.36,0:06:27.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.13,0:06:30.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.34,0:06:31.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去洗手间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.44,0:06:33.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.52,0:06:35.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.83,0:06:40.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薰 难道你害怕单独一个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.74,0:06:42.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.04,0:06:44.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都写在脸上了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.12,0:06:48.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说不是了 我这是陪你去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.45,0:06:49.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.00,0:06:54.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是走这边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.41,0:06:57.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.31,0:06:58.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.93,0:07:02.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么死死地贴在我背后
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.98,0:07:04.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 看起来有这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.73,0:07:06.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你多心了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.96,0:07:07.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.02,0:07:11.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的是什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.18,0:07:12.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.39,0:07:14.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纯一 你去看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.19,0:07:16.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真拿你没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.32,0:07:17.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你留在这
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.74,0:07:19.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 我也要一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.61,0:07:44.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.33,0:07:59.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正在准备饭菜 请先去沐浴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.08,0:08:01.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.54,0:08:05.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那待会再见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.59,0:08:06.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.38,0:08:10.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别一个人先回房间 记得在这里等我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.45,0:08:11.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.78,0:08:14.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薰这个胆小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.44,0:08:16.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说谁是胆小鬼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.47,0:08:23.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里环境真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.09,0:08:28.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薰 发生什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.92,0:08:31.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚那边好像有些什…么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.21,0:08:32.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.32,0:08:35.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我出去 变态
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.07,0:08:35.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.41,0:08:38.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢着 别真的走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.06,0:08:45.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是角落的话 也不是不能让你进来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.90,0:09:10.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.85,0:09:11.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到这边…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.31,0:09:13.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.01,0:09:18.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 有猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.99,0:09:20.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我的胸罩还回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.05,0:09:32.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纯一你这个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.22,0:09:42.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天真是糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.77,0:09:46.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只臭猴子 那可是我很喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.22,0:09:51.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好丰盛的饭菜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.45,0:09:54.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.61,0:09:58.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.38,0:10:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先吃哪个好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.09,0:10:08.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好幸福哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.16,0:10:10.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一转眼心情就这么好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.09,0:10:12.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这太好吃了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.33,0:10:16.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.35,0:10:18.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好饱好饱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.11,0:10:23.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃饱之后突然就想睡觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.27,0:10:26.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 薰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.03,0:10:41.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.25,0:10:41.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.41,0:10:45.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我心里有些困惑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.43,0:10:47.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.11,0:10:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎样和纯一交往下去才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.05,0:11:01.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我分不清什么是朋友什么是恋人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.64,0:11:06.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我希望能在这趟旅途中弄明白它
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.75,0:11:08.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是这么想的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.73,0:11:11.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.26,0:11:14.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纯一？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.04,0:11:31.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.59,0:11:35.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.56,0:11:36.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.02,0:11:38.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的钱包呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.85,0:11:42.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我先垫付好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.94,0:11:43.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.55,0:11:47.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎再次光临
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.97,0:11:54.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样 找到钱包没
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.30,0:11:56.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.79,0:12:01.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧 忘在公共电话亭那了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.63,0:12:06.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时我太心急了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.53,0:12:12.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在怎么办 结了账之后我也没剩多少钱了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.56,0:12:14.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.75,0:12:15.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.76,0:12:18.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早知会这样 昨晚就应该直接去车站
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.77,0:12:21.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后等首发电车才对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.53,0:12:25.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时我还没发现钱包没了 能有什么办法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.09,0:12:28.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说 薰也有不对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.15,0:12:28.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.02,0:12:31.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在服务区买一大堆零食
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.08,0:12:31.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把钱都浪费了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.96,0:12:33.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那才不是浪费
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.86,0:12:35.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和限定商品的相逢是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.32,0:12:37.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又要说「过了这个村就没有这个店」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.26,0:12:38.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经听腻这个理由了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.12,0:12:39.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.56,0:12:47.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是从哪边来的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.09,0:12:48.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.91,0:12:52.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薰 确定走那边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.89,0:12:54.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是我的直觉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.37,0:12:57.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直觉？走错了怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.90,0:12:59.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那纯一走另一边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.63,0:13:02.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随你便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.46,0:13:30.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然不该走这边的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.47,0:13:32.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.84,0:13:34.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.06,0:13:36.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疼疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.09,0:13:38.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧 纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.91,0:13:41.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.33,0:13:56.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.14,0:14:09.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种地方有个车站真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.56,0:14:10.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧 薰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.13,0:14:13.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.02,0:14:20.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只臭猴子 那可是我很喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.55,0:14:36.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.97,0:14:39.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么 只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.78,0:14:45.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我没在看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.82,0:14:46.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看是看到了 不对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.04,0:14:48.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重要部分一点都没看到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.55,0:14:49.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纯一你这个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.46,0:14:56.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼 以前好像也发生过这样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.86,0:14:58.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前也发生过？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.17,0:15:00.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以前也做过被女生掌掴的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.11,0:15:01.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 只是错觉而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.81,0:15:05.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 突然笑出来还真是失礼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.51,0:15:07.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看你脸上那个掌印
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.42,0:15:11.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么这么用力打出一个掌印来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.10,0:15:13.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.12,0:15:25.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猜中了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.12,0:15:29.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薰的直觉 你不是说这边有车站吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.99,0:15:35.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.71,0:15:39.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像说了很多过分的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.99,0:15:41.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还一味地责怪纯一你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.00,0:15:44.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 都是因为我丢了钱包
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.65,0:15:48.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 是我坚持要吃鳗鱼茶套餐的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.05,0:15:50.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 就像纯一说的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.14,0:15:53.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我买了太多限定口味的零食
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.03,0:15:55.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.48,0:15:56.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也说得过火了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.93,0:16:00.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.26,0:16:04.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才是 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.15,0:16:06.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.36,0:16:07.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.38,0:16:12.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旅程才一半 快乐地享受后半吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.07,0:16:15.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就让那些不愉快的事随着雨水一起流走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.07,0:16:18.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真会说漂亮话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.72,0:16:29.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雨停了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.76,0:16:30.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雨终于停了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.45,0:16:38.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个 这个车站早就废弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.14,0:16:40.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有巴士来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.64,0:16:50.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,硬币就只剩这些了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.68,0:16:51.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.38,0:16:55.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 这里是橘家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.43,0:16:56.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 美也吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.42,0:16:57.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.18,0:16:57.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美也 其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.01,0:17:01.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说 今早旅行社那边来电话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.17,0:17:04.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不太清楚是怎么回事 但他们道歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.38,0:17:06.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还说 行李就由他们负责保管
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.85,0:17:08.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老哥你忘记拿行李了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.24,0:17:08.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.94,0:17:13.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但美也叫他们发到付邮件送回来 放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.95,0:17:15.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美也考虑得很周到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.42,0:17:16.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.94,0:17:17.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 完全不用担心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.00,0:17:18.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美也 你先听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.92,0:17:20.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来老哥现在在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.04,0:17:21.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.92,0:17:26.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纯一？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.14,0:17:30.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,断掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.95,0:17:42.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去找派出所吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.95,0:17:44.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.89,0:17:46.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薰？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.77,0:17:49.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 难得有机会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.66,0:17:51.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在这里再玩一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.10,0:18:03.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纯一 快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.73,0:18:41.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.51,0:18:42.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.33,0:18:45.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通过这次旅行我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.83,0:18:48.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管我嘴上说什么 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.07,0:18:50.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要和纯一在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.43,0:18:53.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会非常快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.79,0:18:55.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.73,0:18:58.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后也请你多多关照了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.07,0:19:00.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.45,0:19:26.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.68,0:19:30.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.48,0:19:36.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥们 棚町
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.89,0:19:39.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅原？为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.20,0:19:43.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个暑假 我有我的寿司修行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.66,0:19:45.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥们也有自己的男人修行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.54,0:19:46.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.53,0:19:49.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.03,0:19:52.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男人修行进行得还顺利吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.92,0:19:55.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.89,0:19:58.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羡慕死人了 哥们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.39,0:20:01.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要加油了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.19,0:20:04.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.77,0:20:06.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得救了 薰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.90,0:20:08.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直就是绝处逢生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.52,0:20:18.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样 我和纯一的旅行总算告一段落
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.55,0:20:23.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是 这个高中最后的暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.16,0:20:28.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成了我人生中最棒的暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.33,0:20:38.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.47,0:20:40.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薰 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.05,0:20:42.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,橘他还没到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.01,0:20:45.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是来找惠子你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.48,0:20:47.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.71,0:20:49.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事没事 我懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.86,0:20:52.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的 我有话想对惠子你说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.50,0:20:54.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是关于旅行的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.24,0:20:56.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暑假时已经在电话里听腻了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.00,0:20:59.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就别再说了 感谢你的款待
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.32,0:21:02.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是想当面向你说声谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.39,0:21:04.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 惠子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.58,0:21:06.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.43,0:21:08.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你推荐我去旅行那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.14,0:21:10.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.58,0:21:12.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它成了我的一份美好回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.86,0:21:15.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.98,0:21:16.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.05,0:21:17.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.09,0:21:19.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.79,0:21:21.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿着 帮你弄好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.41,0:21:23.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.84,0:21:33.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 很不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.79,0:21:34.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.65,0:21:37.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好 有人帮你做作业
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.15,0:21:38.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又耍花招 哥们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.36,0:21:40.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.55,0:21:42.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.78,0:21:44.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忘记画灯塔了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.80,0:21:46.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失礼一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.85,0:21:47.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 等…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.96,0:21:49.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薰 你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.95,0:21:50.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还问干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.10,0:21:53.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是帮你把画修好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.17,0:21:54.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我不是那个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.95,0:21:56.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.50,0:21:57.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.31,0:21:59.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别在意 别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.21,0:22:02.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这才是真正的我和你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.52,0:22:05.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也对
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.92,0:23:41.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回预告
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.76,0:23:44.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暑假快要结束了 时间过得真快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.87,0:23:47.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,常言道 光阴似箭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.68,0:23:48.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 等…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.34,0:23:51.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说来梅原你去进行寿司的修行了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.19,0:23:54.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 我距离寿司职人又近了一步
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.69,0:23:57.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大人的阶梯也和做寿司一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.80,0:23:59.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须一步一脚印地攀爬
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.04,0:24:00.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那算什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.20,0:24:02.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,橘 原来你在呀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.53,0:24:04.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥们 你别愣在那儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.07,0:24:05.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.47,0:24:06.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.10,0:24:06.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猜疑
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.79,0:24:09.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来 旁白的那个人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
